# =====================================================
# ZephR$ Environment Configuration
# =====================================================
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER share or commit this file - it is in .gitignore.
# =====================================================


# --- Supabase (already set) ---
# SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxxxxxxxx.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJxxxxxxxxxx...


# --- Roblox Withdrawal Bot ---
# Paste the full .ROBLOSECURITY cookie of your bot account below.
#
# HOW TO GET IT:
#   1. Log in to Roblox in your browser using the BOT account.
#   2. Open DevTools (F12) → Application → Cookies → https://www.roblox.com
#   3. Find the cookie named:  .ROBLOSECURITY
#   4. Copy the ENTIRE value (it's very long) and paste it below.
#
# IMPORTANT: This account must have enough Robux to cover withdrawals.
# Keep this file private. Do NOT share it with anyone.
#
ROBLOX_COOKIE=YOUR_.ROBLOSECURITY_COOKIE_HERE
